query:
insert into controller_jobs(live_spec_id, controller_version, status, failures, error)
        values ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
        on conflict (live_spec_id) do update set
            controller_version = $2,
            status = $3,
            failures = $4,
            error = $5,
            updated_at = now()
        where controller_jobs.live_spec_id = $1;
